<h1>JumpStart Data</h1>

<section style="display:grid;align-content:start;gap:3rem">

	<p>JumpStart is a feature of the CMS that allows you to quickly set up a content structure
	by exporting and importing data in a standardized JSON format. This is particularly useful for
	creating new projects or sharing content structures with others. See the
	<a href="docs/jumpstart">JumpStart documentation</a> for more information.</p>

	{% set exportapi = cms.api ~ "/export/jumpstart/" %}

	<div>
		<h3>Export JumpStart Data</h3>
		<p>This will export all of the data currently stored in the CMS into standardized JSON
		file. This can be used in other projects to quickly set up a similar content structure.</p>
		<p><a href="{{ exportapi }}" class="dash-button" download target="_blank">Export JumpStart Data</a></p>
	</div>

</section>
